{{actor|
| type = Power
| name = Creature detection power
| class = PowerScanner
}}[[Classes]]: [[Classes:Inventory|Inventory]]&rarr;[[Classes:Powerup|Powerup]]&rarr;<u>PowerScanner</u><br>


<u>PowerScanner</u> is an internal class. An item of this class is placed in the player's inventory while he is having the effect of Strife's [[Classes:Scanner|Scanner]] item. While in effect, the player's automap will show actors unless the ({{Flag|NOTONAUTOMAP}} flag is used on said actors) as well as map geometry. This is the same effect seen when using the map cheat ("IDDT") twice. Note that currently this powerup will not function unless the player posesses a [[Classes:MapRevealer|MapRevealer]]-type item such as Doom's [[Classes:Allmap|Computer Area Map]].

Like all other [[Classes:Powerup|Powerup]]s items of this class are never used directly. Instead you have to create a new item that inherits from [[Classes:PowerupGiver|PowerupGiver]] to give it to the player.
